Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:31.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,またゲンだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.93,0:02:32.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やめろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:33.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,押えろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:33.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やめろって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:34.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やり返せ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.27,0:02:36.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰か早く止めろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:38.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ゲン　やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:39.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,こら　何してる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:41.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やめんか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:49.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まったく　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:52.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,年上の子を相手に　なんて怪力だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:56.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おまけに癇癪持ちで　手に負えん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:03:00.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今に何やらかすか　末恐ろしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ゲン
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:10.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうしたその顔　またケンカしたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:13.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,相手は誰だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.26,0:03:15.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あっちが悪い　
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:18.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,陰でコソコソ言うからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:21.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,母さんのことか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.83,0:03:23.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,病気なんかウソだって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:27.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おれが嫌いで出て行ったんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:29.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんなわけないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:33.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前がいい子にしてれば　母さんの病気も今に…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:34.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんなのウソだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.24,0:03:39.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おれを産んだせいで　病気になったから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:41.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おれに会いたくないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:42.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ゲン　いいか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:46.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父さんの話をちゃんと聞くんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:52.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前は元気すぎるから　会わせると病気に良くないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:54.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,わかるな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:03:58.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ゲン
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:01.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一体何を見てる　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:02.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,こっちを見ろ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.67,0:04:08.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ゲン
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.91,0:05:00.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だこれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:07.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いろんな色が　ゆらゆら動いて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:10.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まるで　生きてるみたいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,きれいだな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:25.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でもきっと　これは見たらいけないものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:30.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれらと同じもの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,見たと言ったら　叱られる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:51.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,空に人がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:59.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お父ちゃん　あれ天女？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:04.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ゲン　お前…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:08.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何を言ってる　気のせいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:11.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あそこだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんなもの　見ちゃいけない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:19.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんなもの　いやしない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:37.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:42.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この衣　どこにも縫い目が無い
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:51.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,天女の衣には縫い目が無いのだと　草紙で読んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:05.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もしかしてあれは　この衣を捜しているのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:18.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ゲン　もうやめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:19.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やめるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:19.62,TXT JP (O-UP) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何すんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:20.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰か大人呼んでこい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:31.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前がゲンか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:34.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ずいぶんとたくましく育ったもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:38.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:43.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前の赤子の頃に　ちょいと縁があってな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:47.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの貧相な子がここまでになぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:49.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何か用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:52.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,変わった衣がお前の家にあるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:07:58.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれは　
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:01.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺がお前に着せたもんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:11.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,こちらの赤子が　とても体が弱いと聞きましてね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:18.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なるほど　これは心配ですな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:28.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何をしている
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:31.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,特別な衣を着せています
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:35.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この子が生きる力を取り戻すまで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:38.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この衣はこのままにしてください
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.11,0:08:41.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,衣だと　
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:43.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でたらめを言うな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:45.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どこにそんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ゲン　気が付いたか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:53.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,少しこのまま　様子を見てみませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.69,0:08:59.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お礼は　この子が立派に育ってからで構いませんので
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,とまぁ　そういう事だったんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:08.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,少し効果がありすぎたかね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.93,0:09:13.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前　怒ると自分でも力の加減ができんのだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:17.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちっと　蟲切りが必要かもな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:19.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,蟲？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:25.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前は蟲を見る性質が強くなりすぎた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:27.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうすると子供のうちは特に
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:31.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,自分で自分を思い通りにできなかったりする
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:33.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そういうの嫌だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:35.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なら　手ェ貸してみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:39.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それをしたら　
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:42.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれは見えなくなる？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.07,0:09:46.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　嫌なら全部は抜かんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:04.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,出てこんなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:11.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　普通なら指の先からこう…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:14.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おかしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:20.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんたは…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.01,0:10:28.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,息子さん　立派に育ちましたな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:33.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,たくましく育ってくれたのはありがたいが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:35.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いくらか手に負えんところがある
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:39.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの時は藁にもすがる思いだったが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:44.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ゲンがああなったのは　あんたのせいじゃないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:48.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんた一体　あの時ゲンに何をした
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:53.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,本人に口止めされていたのですが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:57.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの時　ここへ来る前に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:10:59.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの子の母親に会いました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:05.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれは　彼女の作ったものですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:33.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだ　あの衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:38.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,きれいな衣ですな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:42.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一体　どこで手に入れたんです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:47.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あなた　この着物が見えるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:58.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これは　私が紡いだ糸で織ったものです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:04.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　私にもその糸が何なのか分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:10.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,急に見えるようになったんです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:18.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,息子を産んだ時　生死を彷徨ってから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:27.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ゆい　　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:30.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ゆい　気が付いたか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.47,0:12:32.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,気分はどうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:35.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,赤ん坊は？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:38.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,無事だよ　立派な男の子だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:43.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,良かった　どこ　会わせて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:49.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ゆい　お前は何日も眠ったままだったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.57,0:12:52.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの子は里へ連れて帰った
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:54.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,近いうちに連れてくるから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.09,0:12:57.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前はまずこっちでしっかり養生しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:01.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,分かったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:15.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　母さん　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:16.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:21.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,私　まるで生まれ変わったみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:28.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まるで世界が違って見えるの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:50.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,草や木はあんなに光を宿してたかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:10.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何　この糸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:15.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　なんてきれい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:23.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前　何してるんだい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:26.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,とてもきれいな糸でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:31.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちょっと気は早いけど　ゲンの晴れ着にいいと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:33.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,糸？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,母さん知ってた？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:39.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここらの木からこんな糸がとれるなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:42.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:47.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんまり無理するんじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:15:00.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ゲン　会いたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:04.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だいぶ顔色はいいみたいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:07.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうです　ゆいの具合は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:12.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それが…少し心配な所がありまして
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:18.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,時々　おかしなことを言って
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:25.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この子も光を帯びている　
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:31.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんて愛おしい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:40.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ゲン　
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:42.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ゲン
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:44.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうしたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:48.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あなた　ゲンが急にぐったりして
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:50.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何があった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:52.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,分からない　
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:56.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この子を撫でたら光る糸が抜けて　それで…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:58.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何を言ってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:00.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,貸せ　早く医者に
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:02.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,私も…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:03.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前が来なくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:46.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まるで脱皮のようでした
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:51.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その時私は　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:53.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれは生きているのだと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:58.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの糸は触れてはいけない何かだったと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:04.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの子はどうなってしまうのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:08.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,こいつは驚いた　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:14.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの糸は我々蟲師が「妖質」と呼ぶものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんたが急に持った
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.94,0:17:20.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今まで見えなかったものを見せる力のことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:24.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それを薬も使わず
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:27.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ただ指で紡げるって話は聞いたことがないが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:32.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それを抜くとどうなるの　あの子は…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:36.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,成長した子供なら　障りはないが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:40.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,赤子のうちは妖質は生きるのに必要な要素だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:43.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほとんどの者が持って生まれる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:49.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,無闇に抜けば　生きる力を失う
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:51.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんな　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:57.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうすれば　あの子は…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:17:59.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一つ望みはある　
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:04.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この衣をあの子に着せれば　あるいは…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:13.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,結果はご存知の通りです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:16.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの子は人一倍逞しく育った
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:20.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,が　少々妖質を持ちすぎた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:25.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,普通なら我々蟲師が薬で抜けるものが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.74,0:18:27.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの子には利かないくらいに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:31.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あなたには信じられない話かもしれませんが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:35.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの子に話して　母親に会わせてみては？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:40.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今　あの子の糸を抜けるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.69,0:18:42.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの子の母親くらいですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:45.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それは無理だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:48.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:54.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,母さん　おれのこと嫌いじゃなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:19:00.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おれ　母さんに会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:06.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ゲン　すまない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:09.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もっと早く
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:12.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,会わせてやるべきだった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:24.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう二年近くこの状態なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:28.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まるで抜け殻のように
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.87,0:19:33.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もっと　早く許してやれてたら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:36.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの後も糸を紡いでたのか　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:39.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,新しい衣を作るために
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:45.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,妖質に触れすぎて　蟲の気を帯びてしまってる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:50.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もっとこっちに注意しとくべきだった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:54.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうした　ゲン
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:57.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺　この人知ってる　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:19:59.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,覚えてるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:00.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:04.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いつも俺を見てる天女だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:08.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,親子は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:12.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,母親の体を里へ連れ帰った
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:19.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,しばらくすると　その体に生気が戻っていった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:23.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お母さん　聞こえる？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:31.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やがて　
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:34.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その天女は姿を消した
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:41.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ある時　すうっと体が軽くなって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:45.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,気が付くと空からあの子を見てたの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:52.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの子がちゃんと育ってて嬉しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:56.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん　ごめんな　ゆい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:00.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ううん　私こそ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:09.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この衣　約束通り頂いて行きます
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:12.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,本当にそれだけでよろしいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.23,0:21:16.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,十分ですよ　これほどの珍品はまたとない　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:21.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの光　まだ見えるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:25.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それがもう全く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:28.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうか　ならそのほうがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:33.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,しかし　だとしたら結局　どうしたもんか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.95,0:21:36.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,強力な薬を開発するしか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:49.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:53.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう　その必要もないのかもな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.36,0:00:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,
